  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThe API endpoint `/eth/v1/beacon/states/head/validators` returns incorrect information for exited slashed validators.\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nRecent master:\r\n\r\n```\r\ngit rev-parse HEAD\r\na741553028e6e1d461e16e12b23f6402b3f7994d\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nState of exited slashed validators are returned as an object:\r\n\r\n```\r\n      {\r\n        \"index\": \"2069\",\r\n        \"balance\": \"30398924771\",\r\n        \"status\": {\r\n          \"ExitedSlashed\": \"25950\"\r\n        },\r\n        \"validator\": {\r\n          \"pubkey\": \"0xb628001e4fd4dc4067c8f49fa90c75553072c61f0c45a7e67bbf84b5cf143f7593be55551eb447629b340fa8ba074855\",\r\n          \"withdrawal_credentials\": \"0x00241e0a3179a16bdd36bcea3c7658c9eb12a1a444b0d67382411a692a1085d2\",\r\n          \"effective_balance\": \"30000000000\",\r\n          \"slashed\": true,\r\n          \"activation_eligibility_epoch\": \"0\",\r\n          \"activation_epoch\": \"0\",\r\n          \"exit_epoch\": \"17763\",\r\n          \"withdrawable_epoch\": \"25950\"\r\n        }\r\n      },\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nState of exited slashed validators should be returned as a simple string:\r\n\r\n```\r\n      {\r\n        \"index\": \"2069\",\r\n        \"balance\": \"30398924771\",\r\n        \"status\": \"ExitedSlashed\",\r\n        \"validator\": {\r\n          \"pubkey\": \"0xb628001e4fd4dc4067c8f49fa90c75553072c61f0c45a7e67bbf84b5cf143f7593be55551eb447629b340fa8ba074855\",\r\n          \"withdrawal_credentials\": \"0x00241e0a3179a16bdd36bcea3c7658c9eb12a1a444b0d67382411a692a1085d2\",\r\n          \"effective_balance\": \"30000000000\",\r\n          \"slashed\": true,\r\n          \"activation_eligibility_epoch\": \"0\",\r\n          \"activation_epoch\": \"0\",\r\n          \"exit_epoch\": \"17763\",\r\n          \"withdrawable_epoch\": \"25950\"\r\n        }\r\n      },\r\n```\r\n",
